<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Authentication</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Login<sp/>Process</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">When<sp/>you<sp/>run<sp/>`penify<sp/>login`,<sp/>the<sp/>tool:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Opens<sp/>your<sp/>default<sp/>web<sp/>browser</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>Redirects<sp/>you<sp/>to<sp/>Penify&apos;s<sp/>login<sp/>page</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>Captures<sp/>the<sp/>authentication<sp/>token<sp/>after<sp/>successful<sp/>login</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>Saves<sp/>the<sp/>token<sp/>in<sp/>`~/.penify`<sp/>file</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>API<sp/>Token<sp/>Storage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">API<sp/>tokens<sp/>are<sp/>stored<sp/>in<sp/>your<sp/>home<sp/>directory<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>`.penify`<sp/>file.<sp/>This<sp/>JSON<sp/>file<sp/>contains:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```json</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>&quot;api_keys&quot;:<sp/>&quot;your-api-token&quot;,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>&quot;llm&quot;:<sp/>{<sp/>&quot;model&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;,<sp/>&quot;api_base&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;,<sp/>&quot;api_key&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;<sp/>},</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>&quot;jira&quot;:<sp/>{<sp/>&quot;url&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;,<sp/>&quot;username&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;,<sp/>&quot;api_token&quot;:<sp/>&quot;...&quot;<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Token<sp/>Precedence</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>Environment<sp/>variable<sp/>`PENIFY_API_TOKEN`<sp/>(highest<sp/>priority)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>Token<sp/>in<sp/>`~/.penify`<sp/>file</highlight></codeline>
